; 01-hello.scm — the smallest cart. Prints a greeting.
;
; Verbs exercised: display, newline.
; Why it's interesting: every language deserves a hello world. This one
; is short enough to read in a breath. It's the doorway.
;
; Run:
;   ./bin/sakura-scheme run carts/tutorial/01-hello.scm

(display "hello — this is Sakura Scheme.")
(newline)
(display "you're about to see what a small language can do.")
(newline)
